Copyright (c) 2025-2026 The Soqucoin Core developers

Original work by Soqucoin: a logarithmic, Merkle-based aggregation scheme that
batches n Dilithium signatures into a compact proof (the basis of the
`CHECKPATAGG` consensus primitive). Licensed under the MIT License; the full
license text is in the repository root `COPYING`.

This module is original Soqucoin work and is not derived from third-party source
code.
